es/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41c99aae33f89e8381793cdf9ea25d421e05a16d","tid":27142,"uid":16783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T17:11:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>岩岩醒起一個<br />\n以前中學放學會去某同學屋企吹水<br />\n咁我地開住電視傾計 電視係做緊多啦a夢<br />\n有位同學就講緊另一位同學壞話<br />\n話咩呢樣唔好，個樣又點點點<br />\n成個陣媽教仔咁樣<br />\n如是者 講左5,6分鐘終於停<br />\n就係停左之後1,2秒 電視傳來大雄定佢老豆把聲<br />\n*你覺唔覺得自己好長氣呀*<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n於是我地成班爆笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有時行街啲路人都會咁樣爆句好似搭嗲嘅說話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n以前同老豆嘈交<br />\n電視都係播緊仔同父母道歉既劇情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"960cbda019f4b63796cb784b27093a66417965d9","tid":27142,"uid":8731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T17:20:27.000Z","msg":"有一次有樣關於電腦既問題唔識整，跟住太攰去左訓教，之後發夢係夢入面整好左，醒返驚唔記得即刻跟住整，跟住真係整返好"},{"pid":"109f7b2e5f871026f8a9913de363e5b1b6e3459b","tid":27142,"uid":13739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T17:31:42.000Z","msg":"一落雨，地下就濕晒"},{"pid":"2be4c5d4e3f2b9f4799c40a6ce2fb3201d94a3ec","tid":27142,"uid":390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T17:38:10.000Z","msg":"去旅行果時搭飛機見到一對情侶好似熟口熟面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後玩左幾日再係極偏遠嘅景點撞到佢<br />\n回程果陣又撞到佢地仲要坐正前面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n返到香港坐巴士返到屋企樓下又再撞到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我諗一開始熟口熟面係因為住同一區見過<br />\n但冇諗到咁多巧合<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6afe4b3b43df795af0c078370e2785584fc8237","tid":27142,"uid":52086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T17:39:23.000Z","msg":"考試𠴱日臨出門前諗住生生性性咪肚痛個肛門就開始嚟料"},{"pid":"5f135909bf1696ffa1a4b008e2cd1834fd23da95","tid":27142,"uid":25134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T17:40:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>每日解鎖手機時嘅時間都會出現11:11一次或2次<br />\n雖然我覺得呢d可能好無聊或不值一提<br />\n但係11:11係每日都陪住我<br />\n唔知係咪巧合定命運安排</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都係 不過我係11:17"},{"pid":"a4f909b673037e6a6df822543b68448646ff2e1e","tid":27142,"uid":8627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T17:41:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔知有冇巴打試過行行下街突然諗起某個朋友<br />\n過一陣就會撞到果個朋友呢?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n諗過心諗緊林宥嘉果首「自然醒」<br />\n跟住下一首即刻播左出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申：隨機播放</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都試過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好記得個首係周杰倫既晴天<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b77a73e852621ea4221db78ec7997d438143d7f","tid":27142,"uid":58732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T17:42:53.000Z","msg":"係英國坐通宵巴士去巴黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 隔離位架個星加坡人知我係香港人就係咁同我吹水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 過兩日係巴黎鐵塔又見到佢"},{"pid":"ba9e6f886647cdf12895195210303faacae71e6d","tid":27142,"uid":390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T17:43:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>每日解鎖手機時嘅時間都會出現11:11一次或2次<br />\n雖然我覺得呢d可能好無聊或不值一提<br />\n但係11:11係每日都陪住我<br />\n唔知係咪巧合定命運安排</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都係 不過我係11:17</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都係 不過我係12:34<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c33324c4279b039dcbf2e10993e747d1c7630186","tid":27142,"uid":14820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T17:48:14.000Z","msg":"細個嗰陣行過地鐵售票機<br />\n突然覺得入面會有錢係到<br />\n之後伸左隻手入去找錢個位拎左個5蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecb0384886eec7248e8b8a905b8200f6e60540a0","tid":27142,"uid":24572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T17:48:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>去旅行果時搭飛機見到一對情侶好似熟口熟面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後玩左幾日再係極偏遠嘅景點撞到佢<br />\n回程果陣又撞到佢地仲要坐正前面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n返到香港坐巴士返到屋企樓下又再撞到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我諗一開始熟口熟面係因為住同一區見過<br />\n但冇諗到咁多巧合<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都試過，冷門景點遇到對情侶，<br />\n佢地當時仲用廣東話討論我地，<br />\n回程機場見返原來搭同一班機。<br />\n隔左幾個月係間餐廳面對面擦身而過，<br />\n大家你眼望我眼，feel 到認得對方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n巴打如果唔係你話同區，我會以為咁都相認<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cc8f2ad0a547ba4de2ebb1f35289ce55bdcff21","tid":27142,"uid":1582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T17:53:20.000Z","msg":"小學嗰陣好鐘意搞咩音樂藝坊<br />\n食飯時間啲老師同學就喺度表演開始虐待大家隻耳<br />\n之後有次有條友表演完吹笛（當時我喺課室睇live)<br />\n個老師做 MC 就問大家知唔知笛多數喺咩場合吹<br />\n我喺課室同同學講<br />\n話吹野呢啲野當然喺廁所做啦<br />\n之後過幾秒之後<br />\n個 MC 就話：「廁所？唔係掛？」<br />\n我同同學嗰陣笑咗出黎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26245becf4bce6e79aa5276404ffd50c3f27823b","tid":27142,"uid":3146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T17:54:27.000Z","msg":"識左一個同自己同一日生日 同年既人 最後發現連時間都一樣"},{"pid":"09e82af8d76fb20ffd9a916c131c2ee0038e7743","tid":27142,"uid":7065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T18:03:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>每日解鎖手機時嘅時間都會出現11:11一次或2次<br />\n雖然我覺得呢d可能好無聊或不值一提<br />\n但係11:11係每日都陪住我<br />\n唔知係咪巧合定命運安排</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我都係喎"},{"pid":"0a374c3955416ae782e824307afd82d1fe61a5e3","tid":27142,"uid":1248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T18:04:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>每日解鎖手機時嘅時間都會出現11:11一次或2次<br />\n雖然我覺得呢d可能好無聊或不值一提<br />\n但係11:11係每日都陪住我<br />\n唔知係咪巧合定命運安排</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都成日見到1111 或者自己生日</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我係4:44"},{"pid":"cec1d3aca20c1ef60a71bcdb347c9823767e4f4c","tid":27142,"uid":54276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T18:07:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好多次事後比人話見到我但根本我冇響果d地方出現過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b55a62a9433bb34b55a474d489592465615c6ac4","tid":27142,"uid":34465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T18:09:36.000Z","msg":"去外國玩嘅時候我呀哥撞到佢老師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa5dc4d2a2670343198807f84942f474b00db23d","tid":27142,"uid":23156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T18:12:50.000Z","msg":"諗起一個人 嗰嗰人就搵我講左一句 <br />\n希望佢都係諗起我<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e94e5372fa354dcaf70ea44cf8745ce927f54e08","tid":27142,"uid":47349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T18:21:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我鐘意既人鐘意我</blockquote>"},{"pid":"531809823033d5f31cf65bb932214b2d43547de1","tid":27142,"uid":8603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T18:21:58.000Z","msg":"每次都完美地避開中獎既六合彩號碼<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f63b994851461d1d76ee2574bc24d610a83db30d","tid":27142,"uid":11338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T18:28:02.000Z","msg":"有日自己哼緊首平時好少唱既歌<br />\n一開instagram 第一個post<br />\n就係個frd自彈自唱既相<br />\nCaption係我當時唱緊既下一句歌詞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54f543c243df935cf614a7d189b1c94652bc75e5","tid":27142,"uid":16783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T18:28:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>好多次事後比人話見到我但根本我冇響果d地方出現過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n阿媽：其實你仲有個孖生兄弟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f48fd44d7ad26f5fafc5b2128c8cea8e129255fb","tid":27142,"uid":16783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T18:28:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有日自己哼緊首平時好少唱既歌<br />\n一開instagram 第一個post<br />\n就係個frd自彈自唱既相<br />\nCaption係我當時唱緊既下一句歌詞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你有冇覺得好似有人望住你咁？"},{"pid":"de82dcc58a2f340b1885be07e9da159509405963","tid":27142,"uid":29148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T18:29:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>老母生左我<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d79287bcdd5354d0802c0ed90837bbb3233bff3d","tid":27142,"uid":24866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T18:30:17.000Z","msg":"趕時間既時候塞車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d50c5b28a6f9da5a0e59f6aae85e2f865490832","tid":27142,"uid":48165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T18:31:35.000Z","msg":"前排仆街芒好Hit個陣我同女朋友行緊街無玩，跟住佢無拿拿勁大聲講左句<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">雞蛋六隻！</span>，然後隔離有個人落車講左句一樣既野，但係落車個個無可能聽到。我女朋友都問我做乜鳩無拿拿講雞蛋六隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81878701ca547310b0523dcec1f38cd1a7b14085","tid":27142,"uid":51075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T18:32:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>唔知有冇巴打試過行行下街突然諗起某個朋友<br />\n過一陣就會撞到果個朋友呢?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n試過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同個朋友行緊街 講緊個好耐冇聯絡嘅中同<br />\n唔夠10秒撞到佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都試過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同好耐無見既小學同學 講開另一個<br />\n跟住轉個角就撞到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n試過係巴士忽然諗起個朋友<br />\n下秒巴士埋站佢就上車了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"195801baf35869411f2287148d5e0415ca3e82d3","tid":27142,"uid":16783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T18:33:44.000Z","msg":"試過有人講完啲恐怖野<br />\n下一秒就行雷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a37870c8a766a32ab792a4f46ea3595063144f6e","tid":27142,"uid":13136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T18:35:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>前排仆街芒好Hit個陣我同女朋友行緊街無玩，跟住佢無拿拿勁大聲講左句<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">雞蛋六隻！</span>，然後隔離有個人落車講左句一樣既野，但係落車個個無可能聽到。我女朋友都問我做乜鳩無拿拿講雞蛋六隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有冇人明？"},{"pid":"dc64b7cf03adf5051e8ff50c9367d24ff7b32aea","tid":27142,"uid":16783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T18:36:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>小學嗰陣好鐘意搞咩音樂藝坊<br />\n食飯時間啲老師同學就喺度表演開始虐待大家隻耳<br />\n之後有次有條友表演完吹笛（當時我喺課室睇live)<br />\n個老師做 MC 就問大家知唔知笛多數喺咩場合吹<br />\n我喺課室同同學講<br />\n話吹野呢啲野當然喺廁所做啦<br />\n之後過幾秒之後<br />\n個 MC 就話：「廁所？唔係掛？」<br />\n我同同學嗰陣笑咗出黎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n細個已經識呢啲野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nbtw <br />\n前幾日食住m記睇達哥<br />\n飲完可樂嗝左啖氣出黎之後<br />\n達哥就話 邊個係度嗝氣呀 咁核突<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcb87542393a7c37d6d31b15416433f57460cd20","tid":27142,"uid":16783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T18:38:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>前排仆街芒好Hit個陣我同女朋友行緊街無玩，跟住佢無拿拿勁大聲講左句<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">雞蛋六隻！</span>，然後隔離有個人落車講左句一樣既野，但係落車個個無可能聽到。我女朋友都問我做乜鳩無拿拿講雞蛋六隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有冇人明？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我明呀 但想知關仆街芒咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋你提完又要話自己無玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c41ce536b5192f37d8b71f8240dd05503c4d0c60","tid":27142,"uid":24116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T18:50:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>前排仆街芒好Hit個陣我同女朋友行緊街無玩，跟住佢無拿拿勁大聲講左句<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">雞蛋六隻！</span>，然後隔離有個人落車講左句一樣既野，但係落車個個無可能聽到。我女朋友都問我做乜鳩無拿拿講雞蛋六隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有冇人明？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我重複睇左三次都唔明<br />\n之後就睇到你個回覆<br />\n咁應該唔係我問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cf7ddbaec9478071a7a584816854784e0e9eda5","tid":27142,"uid":47496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T23:48:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>每日解鎖手機時嘅時間都會出現11:11一次或2次<br />\n雖然我覺得呢d可能好無聊或不值一提<br />\n但係11:11係每日都陪住我<br />\n唔知係咪巧合定命運安排</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我都係喎</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好原都唔少人同我一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"829029ff19801007ffe0db4d797a86f2b25dae6f","tid":27142,"uid":48165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T23:57:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>前排仆街芒好Hit個陣我同女朋友行緊街無玩，跟住佢無拿拿勁大聲講左句<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">雞蛋六隻！</span>，然後隔離有個人落車講左句一樣既野，但係落車個個無可能聽到。我女朋友都問我做乜鳩無拿拿講雞蛋六隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有冇人明？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我明呀 但想知關仆街芒咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋你提完又要話自己無玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n手上無玩既，跟住有隻精靈係勁似雞蛋同埋有6隻，我同女朋友都叫佢雞蛋六隻。點知有個人落車佢都係手上無電話玩緊，佢又一齊講左雞蛋六隻出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 原來我表達能力都幾差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58a533cae65f61abb44b3e854b4a9009f19ab63b","tid":27142,"uid":22676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T00:10:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔知有冇巴打試過行行下街突然諗起某個朋友<br />\n過一陣就會撞到果個朋友呢?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有呀<br />\n成日都係咁"},{"pid":"e6643cb2dd8a966da522287d168f320ff8330ac7","tid":27142,"uid":22676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T00:12:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>搭地鐵企起門邊諗起個ex, 一到站道門打開就見到佢，心都離一離</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我又試過呀<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e2b3695d8be9d98387b94657490e6352d36afec","tid":27142,"uid":1593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T00:14:33.000Z","msg":"經常性發生，男友打俾我，我又同時間打俾男友<br />\n撞到應一應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9954b12eb8d607afadd537654dd29e5c031aa7b1","tid":27142,"uid":50815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T00:16:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔知有冇巴打試過行行下街突然諗起某個朋友<br />\n過一陣就會撞到果個朋友呢?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有呀<br />\n成日都係咁</blockquote><br />\n我覺得好神秘<br />\n好似腦電波傳送咁"},{"pid":"fb5c9574daff1dc6367d0527c19de8d1e2131717","tid":27142,"uid":36478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T00:17:46.000Z","msg":"入咗呢個Post"},{"pid":"70a7d197132fb4855df6296c135ff18801f88f67","tid":27142,"uid":19493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T00:20:34.000Z","msg":"想溝一條女<br />\n約唔到出嚟<br />\n之後瘋狂係啲古怪地方撞到佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家佢以為我跟蹤佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9338eaeca84894f98abddae733b76cf70e310684","tid":27142,"uid":10325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T00:35:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想溝一條女<br />\n約唔到出嚟<br />\n之後瘋狂係啲古怪地方撞到佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家佢以為我跟蹤佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6d7fe9a22648bb8ac9719e80577703868ee5562","tid":27142,"uid":19493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T00:40:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>想溝一條女<br />\n約唔到出嚟<br />\n之後瘋狂係啲古怪地方撞到佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家佢以為我跟蹤佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n心血來潮想兜路 就係窄巷撞到正一正"},{"pid":"fa2c23ac39458830b